{"tid":461100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ios 11連打字都冇test就出街！字母大階「I」會自動被更改成「A [?]」","createTime":"2017-11-07T08:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T14:09:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"24c689a5fb60b4b997c60e5492f5f9d742d3ba4f","tid":461100,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:56:29.000Z","msg":"十一月 7, 2017<br />\n<br />\n有部份 iOS 用戶在討論區反映升級到 iOS 11.1 之後，輸入英文字母大階「I」會自動被更改成「A [?]」，當中的 [?] 是一個 Unicode 空白符號。蘋果已從用戶支援論壇中得到有關報告，現時正進行修正。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ios11predictivetextbug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Fios11predictivetextbug.jpg&h=390c2c91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次發生問題的是部份 iPhone、iPad 等安裝了 iOS 11.0.3 以及 11.1 後英文輸入法的自動修正功能。在輸入英文字母「I」時，會自動被更改成 A、#、! 任何一個符號再加一個以「 [?] 」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/11/07/ioskeyboard/software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2Fioskeyboard%2Fsoftware%2F&d=MEmtNKNP7a1E2IzQ75qGIkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=40cfd034\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/11/07/ioskeyboard/software/</a>"},{"pid":"7e2e6b5543402bfb755590f1cd5405d58d34ca91","tid":461100,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:56:44.000Z","msg":"rubbish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae80b36b0e90785a45407cf7e735a2892f172a8","tid":461100,"uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T09:00:42.000Z","msg":"疑似Apple IT<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20150425/large/1429937074_40f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg